{
  "stem": "812.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There are no words that can describe that-- the constant foul odor, the horror, the-- the-- the fear, and the constant death that was surrounding us.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We would trip over the dead.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was common to see people just fall and die, and-- or just not to wake up, or just to lay down because they-- they were weak and they couldn't go on anymore, and the next minute, they were gone.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] As I said, Bergen-Belsen was not an extermination camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were crematorium.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had the high chimneys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "To this day, when I see a chimney, I cringe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, they had to burn the dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were so many.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But it was not an extermination camp, per se.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the Germans-- we just-- the Germans couldn't get rid of us fast enough.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So it was decided-- towards April of '45-- to send us to what we thought would be Auschwitz, because Auschwitz, as it's-- as an extermination camp, would be the solution for the majority of us, or for all of us.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We were-- those who were able to walk were walked to the station again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were put on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This was a very long train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were some cattle cars, some so-called passenger cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I remember we were in an old passenger car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I believe we were with my-- my father and my brother, my mother and I-- we were together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We were on this train for two full weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Actually, it was 13 days-- 13 days and 13 nights, and this without food and without water.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It is amazing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It is miraculous how any one of us could have survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The train went very slowly.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
